{
  "stem": "4345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was at one point low tide, where you could swim along with the-- with the-- with the wagon and the horses.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we crossed this river.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then once we got there, it was already-- I-- when I said, about six weeks, we were met by the German tanks over there past the-- past the water.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We took a different way to go home, you know, and we were forced by the Germans to go back.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I don't know what way we took.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't ask me because I was too young even to know what was-- you know, how-- how, what, when.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as we are going back, you know, under the German guards with, you know, with their bayonets ready to-- you know, I could see dead bodies on the floor, laying on the ground, and I couldn't imagine why-- why there's dead bodies.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, Momma, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I see dead people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, I said, Mommy, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This person is moving.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have to go help.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So mommy said, Mila, look, don't-- [GERMAN]-- don't look, she said to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Just be quiet and don't talk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because she was afraid that they-- they took people off the wagons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They took people out of the houses, and they just shot them, just like what you saw in When I looked at this-- at these pictures, this is what I saw myself.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is what I lived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I knew what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew that the Germans were shooting them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These people were from other towns and even from-- people that I knew, I wouldn't know if I knew them because I really didn't know everybody.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew people from my street, mostly, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
